title: Apple Service Diagnostic Disc - Intel Macs
description:
I think someone tried to upload this a few days ago.

This is ASD dual boot version 3S116.

Supports the following machines:-

MacBook (13-inch Mid 2007) 
Mac Pro 8x 
MacBook Pro (15-inch Core 2 Duo) 
MacBook Pro (17-inch Core 2 Duo) 
MacBook (Late 2006) 
MacBook Pro (15-inch 2.4/2.2GHz) 
MacBook Pro (17-inch 2.4GHz) 
iMac (24-inch Mid 2007) 
iMac (20-inch Mid 2007) 
Mac mini (Mid 2007) 
iMac (Early 2006 17-inch) 
iMac (Early 2006 20-inch) 
MacBook Pro 
Mac mini (Early 2006) 
MacBook Pro (17-inch) 
MacBook (13-inch) 
iMac (Mid 2006 17-inch) 
Mac Pro 
iMac (17-inch Late 2006) 
iMac (24-inch) 
iMac (17-inch Late 2006 CD) 
iMac (20-inch late 2006) 

The image file must be burned to a dvd. 

There are also .pdf files for Test Results Guide, Read Me Service, User Guide and Burning to Disc.
